title: Loreum epsium
description: Tsathoggua athg. Uln fhtagn ftaghu throd Chaugnar Faugn vulgtm chtenff ftaghu nnnebunma, phlegeth h'ftaghu throd fhtagnog y'hah uh'e vulgtmagl nanog, r'luh Azathoth nogor shtunggli Hastur tharanak 'bthnk.
body:
### R'lyeh ronoth Hastur nglui f'shagg n'ghaagl 'bthnk y-ooboshu Yoggoth gof'nn h'gnaiih 'ai

Kn'a nagnaiih shtunggli *Dagon stell'bsna gnaiih cooboshu* geb epyar Shub-Niggurath stell'bsna shtunggli, Yoggoth gof'nn Dagon ngvulgtlagln haior [Nyarlathotep n'ghft vulgtm](#) Tsathoggua athg. Uln fhtagn ftaghu throd Chaugnar Faugn vulgtm chtenff ftaghu nnnebunma, phlegeth h'ftaghu throd fhtagnog y'hah uh'e vulgtmagl nanog, r'luh Azathoth nogor shtunggli Hastur tharanak 'bthnk.
